divs: Sighting Detailswas walking home from my girlfriends work and noticed smoke trail in sky. thought it was just airplane trails, then saw a small glowing orb buzzing back and forth in near 180 degree change of direction. I went and got my phone and filmed the object as well as took pictures. went out 20 minutes later there were two separate paths. went out 5 minutes later the orb vanished. in films you can hear one of my neighbors go OMG!
Summary: orb travelled back and forth leaving criss cross smoke trails that turned into tiny loops and odd winged like trail
